headline: West Pharmaceutical Services (WST) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of healthcare products company West Pharmaceutical Services (NYSE:WST) jumped 3.1% in the afternoon session after a research note from KeyBanc Capital Markets indicated positive momentum in the bioprocessing sector following an industry conference.
